Package: fidelioDiagnostics
Type: Package
Title: FIDELIO Diagnostics and Shiny Utilities
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Paola", family = "Rocchi", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "paola.rocchi@cmcc.it")
Description: Internal utilities to extract results from FIDELIO GDX files, 
    compute derived indicators, validate outputs, and serve precomputed data 
    to a Shiny dashboard. Provides a declarative registry of symbols, 
    a YAML-based configuration layer, and a single entrypoint 
    `run_pipeline()` for reproducible diagnostics.
